### Pre Scripts
While you can have tasks that are dedicated scripts, it can become a bit noisy, and we want our diagrams to convey a clear sense of the business logic and rules.  For this reason it is also possible to add scripts to all Task types - using Pre and Post Scripts.   This manual task contains a pre-script that also calculated PI using the Leibnizâ€™s formula.  The value is ...

